otland.  See also  Annis ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Agnes De Fransham was born in 1397, in Cranworth, Norfolk, England, United Kingdom as the daughter of Gilbert De Fransham and Agnes. She married Edmund De Swathing I before 1418, in Cranworth, Norfolk, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 1 son. She died in 1418, in her hometown, at the age of 21."},"et":{"1397–1418":"1397–1418","1390–Male":"1390–Surnud","1428–Male":"1428–Surnud","–1370":"–1370","–1404":"–1404","1404":"1404","1397":"1397","1370":"1370","before 1418":"enne 1418","1418":"1418","1428":"1428","1390":"1390","Cranworth, Norfolk, England":"Cranworth, Norfolk, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Cranworth, Norfolk, England, United Kingdom":"Cranworth, Norfolk, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1397–1418":"1397–1418","1390–Male":"1390–Kuollut","1428–Male":"1428–Kuollut","–1370":"–1370","–1404":"–1404","1404":"1404","1397":"1397","1370":"1370","before 1418":"ennen vuotta 1418","1418":"1418","1428":"1428","1390":"1390","Cranworth, Norfolk, England":"Cranworth, Norfolk, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Cranworth, Norfolk, England, United Kingdom":"Cranworth, Norfolk, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1397–1418":"1397–1418","1390–Male":"1390–Décédé","1428–Male":"1428–Décédé","–1370":"–1370","–1404":"–1404","1404":"1404","1397":"1397","1370":"1370","before 1418":"avant 1418","1418":"1418","1428":"1428","1390":"1390","Cranworth, Norfolk, England":"Cranworth, Norfolk, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Cranworth, Norfolk, England, United Kingdom":"Cranworth, Norfolk, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Agnes De Fransham est née en 1397, à Cranworth, Norfolk, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, fille de Gilbert De Fransham et Agnes. Elle a épousé Edmund De Swathing I avant 1418, à Cranworth, Norfolk, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils. Elle est décédée en 1418, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 21 ans."},"de":{"1397–1418":"1397–1418","1390–Male":"1390–Verstorben","1428–Male":"14